	<td>Peak calling</td>
	<td>
	  <ol>
		 <li>Assessing ChIP-Seq quality.</li>
	    <li>Normalizing ChIP-Seq data.</li>
	    <li>Diversity of peak-calling approaches.</li>
	    <li>MACS algorithm.</li>
	    <li>Sicer algorithm.</li>
	    <li>Impact of peak-calling parameters on the number and quality of the peaks.</li>
	    <li>Further reading.</li>
	  </ol>
