	<td>Detecting motifs in ChIP-seq peaks (talk)</td>
	<td rowspan='2'>

	  <ol>
	    <li>String-based motif discovery</li>
	    <li>Comparing discovered motifs with transcription factor databases.</li>
	    <li>Predicting binding sites</li>
	    <li>Estimating peak quality on the basis of motif enrichment</li>
	  </ol>
	</td>
	<td rowspan='2'>
	  <b>Tutorial</b>
	  <ol start="3">
