	      <li>ChIPMunk (on <a target='_blank' href="http://nebula.curie.fr/">Nebula</a>)</li>
	  </ol>

	  <p><b>Peak-motifs protocol</b></p>
	  <p>Thomas-Chollier, M., Darbo, E., Herrmann, C., Defrance,
	    M., Thieffry, D. & van Helden, J. (2012). A complete workflow
